subject: Rajasthan History
question_en: Which famous fort in Rajasthan was built by Maharaja Jai Singh?
question_hi: राजस्थान में महाराजा जैसिंग ने किया गया किस पवन?
explanation_en:
Mehrangarh Fort, built by Maharaja Jai Singh, is the answer. It is a famous fort in Jodhpur, Rajasthan.
